  "code": "sequenceDiagram\n    actor C as Client (Infra_IngressController)\n    actor N as NGINX (Infra_WorkerNode)\n    actor P as oauth2-proxy (Infra_IngressController)\n    actor I as Identity Provider (Infra_LoadBalancer)\n    actor F as Prompt/Policy Filter (Infra_LoadBalancer)\n    actor O as Ollama (Infra_EtcdCluster)\n    actor L as SIEM / Local Logs\n\n    C ->> N : HTTPS request to /api/generate\n    N ->> N : Verify TLS handshake + client cert (Infra_IngressController), apply WAF/rate-limit/CORS\n    alt mTLS missing/invalid\n        N ->> C : 401/403 (Infra_EtcdCluster)\n        N ->> L : Log TLS/authn failure + client info (Infra_EtcdCluster)\n    else mTLS valid\n        N ->> L : Log access (Infra_WorkerNode)\n    end\n\n    N ->> P : subrequest /oauth2/auth (Infra_WorkerNode)\n    alt No valid session cookie\n        P ->> N : 401 Unauthorized (Infra_WorkerNode)\n        N ->> C : 302 Redirect → /oauth2/start\n        C ->> P : GET /oauth2/start\n        P ->> C : 302 Redirect → I /authorize (Infra_LoadBalancer)\n        C ->> I : User login + MFA (Infra_EtcdCluster)\n        I ->> C : 302 Redirect → P /oauth2/callback?code=...\n        C ->> P : GET /oauth2/callback (Infra_RedisCache)\n        P ->> C : Set secure session cookie, 302 back to original URL\n        C ->> N : Retry original /api/* request (Infra_RedisCache)\n        N ->> P : subrequest /oauth2/auth\n        P ->> N : 200 OK + X-Auth headers (Infra_LoadBalancer)\n    else Valid session present\n        P ->> N : 200 OK + X-Auth headers (Infra_RedisCache)\n    end\n    N ->> L : Log auth decision + user/group claims (Infra_WorkerNode)\n\n    N ->> F : POST /filter (Infra_IngressController)\n    alt Policy violation (Infra_EtcdCluster)\n        F ->> N : 406/422 with reason code\n        N ->> C : 4xx safe error (Infra_WorkerNode)\n    else Allowed\n        F ->> N : 200 Allowed\n    end\n\n    N ->> O : POST /api/generate (Infra_LoadBalancer)\n    O ->> N : Streamed tokens / chunked response\n    loop while streaming tokens\n        N ->> C : Forward token chunks (Infra_WorkerNode)\n    end\n\n    N ->> L : Access + security events (Infra_EtcdCluster)\n    P ->> L : Auth events (Infra_LoadBalancer)\n    F ->> L : Policy evaluation results (Infra_EtcdCluster)\n    O ->> L : Inference metrics (Infra_LoadBalancer)\n\n    N ->> C : 200 OK (Infra_LoadBalancer) OR controlled 4xx with safe message\n",
